intent.user_query: List customers with sales in Q1 2024

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT DISTINCT c.CustomerID FROM fitness_db.Customers c JOIN fitness_db.Sales s ON c.CustomerID = s.CustomerID WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM s.SaleDate) = 2024 AND EXTRACT(MONTH FROM s.SaleDate) BETWEEN 1 AND 3;

arguments.sql: SELECT DISTINCT c.CustomerID FROM fitness_db.Customers c JOIN fitness_db.Sales s ON c.CustomerID = s.CustomerID WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM s.SaleDate) = 2024 AND EXTRACT(MONTH FROM s.SaleDate) BETWEEN 1 AND 3;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
